    "**Dataset:** [Kaggle — Credit Card Fraud Detection](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mlg-ulb/creditcardfraud)  \n",
    "**Goal:** Build a machine learning model to detect fraudulent transactions, and understand the key patterns that distinguish fraud from legitimate activity.\n",
