    "## 6. Threshold Tuning\n",
    "\n",
    "By default, models classify as fraud if probability > 0.5. But in payments fraud, we may want to **lower the threshold** to catch more fraud (higher recall), accepting more false alarms.\n",
    "\n",
    "This is a business decision: what's the cost of a missed fraud vs. a false alarm?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "id": "a9b0c1d2",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
